ically combines their losses. We test our approach on three datasets of\nhistopathological images. Our experiments demonstrate that it leads to better\nsegmentation results in these datasets, compared to its counterparts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Jan 2020 08:09:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 21 May 2020 10:22:35 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 25 Nov 2020 11:18:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-26"}
