ication, we derive the full set of two-loop rational\ncounterterms for QED in the $R_{\\xi}$-gauge.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Jan 2020 15:19:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 9 Feb 2020 18:42:17 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 4 Jun 2020 11:24:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-24"}
