or finding new\ntopological materials and to narrow down candidates for experimental synthesis\nand characterization.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Jan 2020 15:21:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 11 Feb 2020 16:10:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-08"}
